author: Robb M. Stewart
title: Origin Energy to Raise Over a Billion Dollars
text:
MELBOURNE, Australia—Squeezed by the slump in oil prices and a mountain of debt built up in a bet on Asia’s demand for natural gas, Origin Energy Ltd. announced plans to raise billions of dollars from shareholders, along with cost cuts and asset sales.
